Package: geoprofiler
Title: Distance Along Profile
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Tobias", "Stephan", , "tobias.stephan1@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9290-014X"))
Description: Toolset to measures distances along lines defined by a
    direction or create swath profiles. Also provides functions to create
    swath profiles. Method are based on Coordinate rotation algortihm by
    Schaeben et al. (2024) <doi:10.1002/mma.9823>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://tobiste.github.io/geoprofiler/
